<facsimile><graphic url="https://www.e-manuscripta.ch/i3f/v20/1079306/manifest"/></facsimile><text><body><div type="letter">
<pb facs="1079307" n="1"/>
<opener><salute>Celeberrimo at<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> Doctissimo Viro
             <lb/>Petro Antonio <rs key="pers_DE-588-102552517" type="person">Michelotto</rs>
<lb/><abbr>S. P. D.</abbr>
<lb/><choice><abbr>Joh.</abbr><expan>Johanni</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Bernoull<choice><orig><g ref="#j">j</g></orig><reg>i</reg></choice></rs></salute></opener>
<p>Novissimas <rs key="B_1722-08-01_991170515149305501" type="letter">Litteras</rs><note type="editorial">Pietro Antonio Michelotti an Johann I Bernoulli, vom 1. August 1722</note> Tuas, Vir <choice><abbr>Cl.</abbr><expan>Clarissime</expan></choice> <rs key="place_GEO-2988507" type="place">Luteti<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice></rs> ad me
             <lb/>datas <choice><abbr>d.</abbr><expan>die</expan></choice> 1. <choice><abbr>Aug.</abbr><expan>Augusti</expan></choice> accepi hic <rs key="place_GEO-2991214" type="place">Mulhusii</rs>,<note type="editorial">Siehe auch den Brief von  1722.07.28  an Varignon, in dem Joh. I B. von seinem Aufenthalt in Mühlhausen berichtet. Unter anderem schreibt er, er halte sich mit seinem älteren Sohn (Nic. II B.) dort auf, was Rückschlüsse auf den Schreiber des Briefentwurf erlaubt.</note> ubi adhuc co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>o<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ror et in quod oppidum concessi ut me subtraherem
         <lb/>aliquamdiu negotiis tam publicis quam privatis ad
             <lb/>potandas aquas minerales <rs key="place_GEO-2659224" type="place">Fabarienses</rs><!-- sachtag --><note type="editorial">Mineralwasser aus Bad Pfäfers.</note> (quas huc depor<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tari curavi) omni qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> licet tranquillitate et otio. Noli
         <lb/>qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>rere quem in finem ad has potiones adstrin<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>xerim me, Tu qui Medicus es facile conjectabis,
         <lb/>id me non fecisse animi gratia, quorsum enim
         <lb/>ingrata illa et fastidiosa aquarum ingurgitatio,
         <lb/>nisi eam summa necessitas postularet.
         <lb/>Utor certe per aliquot jam annos valetudine
         <lb/>usque adeo dubia et vacillante, ut nullos fere
         <lb/>amplius animi labores ferre possim et tantum
         <lb/>non omnino meditationibus mathematicis
         <lb/>valedicere cogar. En habes, Vir Illustrissime, diuturni
         <pb facs="1079308" n="2"/>
<lb/>mei silentii causam, quo factum, ut ad
         <lb/><rs key="B_1722-01-23_991170515149605501" type="letter">epistolam</rs><note type="editorial">Pietro Antonio Michelotti an Johann I Bernoulli, vom 23. Januar 1722</note> Tuam bene longam pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>terito jam
         <lb/>mense Januario ad me exaratam nondum respon<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>derim ne<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> ob rerum multitudinem per litteras
         <lb/>respondere queam, scilicet non permittit viri<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>
         <lb/>attritio ut long<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> scriptioni man<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> admoveam,
         <lb/>et multo minus ut me immergam litterarum
         <lb/>reciprocationi nullum finem habitur<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> de
         <lb/>argumento quopiam, quod nisi ad amussim
         <lb/>utrinque controversi<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> punctum definia<choice><orig><g ref="#tur">&#xf199;</g></orig><reg>tur</reg></choice>, facile in
         <lb/>rixarum perpetuationem facessit non sine magno
         <lb/>non tam temporis quam quietis mihi adeo necessari<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
         <lb/>dispendio, quare satius duco ut e<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> de re Tecum
         <lb/>agam oretenus, id quod commod<choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> fieri poterit
    <lb/>quando in reditu Tuo nostros Lares<!-- orttag --> salutaveris,
         <lb/>quo casu Tibi utrumque et hospitium et mensam
         <lb/>meam offero, quibus quamdiu lubuerit uti fruique
         <lb/>poteris. Quod nunc attinet ad binas Tuas
         <lb/>difficultates mihi propositas, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> sibi mutuo
         <lb/>contradicunt sponte diluen<choice><orig><g ref="#tur">&#xf199;</g></orig><reg>tur</reg></choice> et evanescent
         <pb facs="1079309" n="3"/>
<lb/>si prope perceperis modum premendi quo gaudent
         <lb/>fluida quando <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> vi quadam urgen<choice><orig><g ref="#tur">&#xf199;</g></orig><reg>tur</reg></choice> abstrahendo
         <lb/>nempe ab eorum gravitate; adverte qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>so mentem
         <lb/>ad naturam fluidi elastici in aliquo vase in<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>clusi, e. gr. aëris in recipiente quodam condensati; Intelligis
         <lb/>haud dubi<choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice>, qualemcunque habeat figuram<!-- figurtag -->
<lb/>recipiens, aërem sese dilatare conantem
         <lb/>quaquavers<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> vim suam in latera recipientis
         <lb/><choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>qualiter exerere<choice><orig>)</orig><reg>,</reg></choice> ita ut pars unaqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>que su<choice><orig><g ref="#per">&#42833;</g></orig><reg>per</reg></choice>fi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ciei intern<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> participet de ista pressione
         <lb/>pro ratione magnitudinis su<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> in locis
         <lb/>recipientis angustioribus <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice><choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> ac in amplio<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ribus, quantitas enim hujus pressionis unic<choice><orig><g ref="#eacut">é</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice>
         <lb/>dependet <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> vi elastica qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> per totam cavitatem
         <lb/>recipientis est <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>quabilis et uniformis, unde
         <lb/>necessari<choice><orig><g ref="#ograv">ò</g></orig><reg>o</reg></choice> partes du<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>quales su<choice><orig><g ref="#per">&#42833;</g></orig><reg>per</reg></choice>ficiei intern<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
         <lb/>ubicunque suman<choice><orig><g ref="#tur">&#xf199;</g></orig><reg>tur</reg></choice>, sustinebunt et patien<choice><orig><g ref="#tur">&#xf199;</g></orig><reg>tur</reg></choice>
         <lb/><choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>quales pressiones; h<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>c ratio est, cur mercurius
         <lb/>in barometro in eadem h<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>ret altitudine sive in
         <lb/>conclavi clauso existat sive sub dio<note type="editorial">"sub dio" = unter freiem Himmel.</note> colloce<choice><orig><g ref="#tur">&#xf199;</g></orig><reg>tur</reg></choice> et
         <lb/>aëri libero expona<choice><orig><g ref="#tur">&#xf199;</g></orig><reg>tur</reg></choice>, etenim utrobi<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> aër vi sua
         <pb facs="1079310" n="4"/>
<lb/>elastic<choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> mercurium subjectum et in inferiori vasculo
         <lb/>contentum <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>qualiter premit et per tubum sursum
         <lb/>versus urget. Hoc ita intellecto haud <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>gr<choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> perci<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>pies porro fluidum vel liquorem quemcunque
         <lb/>(seposita gravitatis actione) contentum in canali
    <lb/><formula>BADF</formula>,<figure facs="1079310_01.png" hand="pers_DE-588-118509969"/> cujus orificium <formula>AD</formula>, ab
         <lb/>initio clausum suppona<choice><orig><g ref="#tur">&#xf199;</g></orig><reg>tur</reg></choice>, si
         <lb/>urge<choice><orig><g ref="#tur">&#xf199;</g></orig><reg>tur</reg></choice> <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> vi quadam per alter<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>
         <lb/>orificium <formula>BF</formula> admot<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice>, percipies inquam hanc
         <lb/>vim statim per totam liquoris massam diffundi,
         <lb/>ita ut anime<choice><orig><g ref="#tur">&#xf199;</g></orig><reg>tur</reg></choice> tanquam <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> vi imsita elastica in
         <lb/>modum aëris condensati, <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> quo proin non differt,
         <lb/>nisi quod vis illa in aëre sit naturalis, sed adven<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>titia in hoc liquore; ratio vero agendi et latera
         <lb/>premendi in utroque est eadem, hinc ex pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>ce<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>dentibus colliges, cujuscun<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> sit figur<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice><!-- figurtag --> canalis
         <lb/><formula>BADF</formula>, sive conic<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> sive alius<note type="editorial">Weniger gebräuchliche Form des Genitivs von alius, alterius.</note>, partes laterum
         <lb/><formula>mn</formula> et <formula>pq</formula> <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>quales, debere etiam pati <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>quales
         <lb/>pressiones <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> liquore undique exitum moliente
         <lb/>instar aëris elastici; nec est quod dicas parti
         <lb/><formula>mn</formula> majorem applicari columellam liquoris
         <lb/>quam parti <formula>pq</formula>; h<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> enim columell<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> non aliter
         <pb facs="1079311" n="5"/>
<lb/>agunt quam recipiendo <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> particulis liquoris con<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tiguis et transmittendo ab altera in alteram vim
         <lb/>expansivam eo fere modo quo sana ratio et experi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>entia docet, vim qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> primo globulo <formula>c</formula><note type="editorial">Die Buchstaben c/C und d/D bzw. C und  sind in der Figur und im Text nicht einheitlich gross oder klein geschrieben. In der Transkription wurden sie einheitlich als Minuskel wiedergegeben.</note> seriei globulor<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>
    <lb/><figure facs="1079311_01.png" hand="pers_DE-588-118509969"/><formula>cd</formula> horizontaliter juxta se invicem
         <lb/>in recta linea positorum imprimi<choice><orig><g ref="#tur">&#xf199;</g></orig><reg>tur</reg></choice>
         <lb/>secundum eandem directionem <formula>Ec</formula>, eandem statim
         <lb/>imprimi objecto obici <formula>AB</formula>, dum nimirum per omnes
         <lb/>intermedios globulos ab uno in alterum in instanti
         <lb/>transmitti<choice><orig><g ref="#tur">&#xf199;</g></orig><reg>tur</reg></choice>; intelligis autem, opinor, multitudinem
         <lb/>globulorum nihil omnino ad rem facere; sustinebit
         <lb/>quippe obex <formula>AB</formula> eandem semper pressionem,
